{"id":339761,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/03/【图说天朝】米歇尔访西安-安保特警打晕导游/","date":"2014-03-25T02:20:50Z","modified":"2014-03-26T02:44:17Z","title":"【图说天朝】米歇尔访西安 安保特警打晕导游","content":"<p>3月24日，美国第一夫人米歇尔.奥巴马继续访华行程。她在西安参观兵马俑时，中方安保人员为了清场而将一名当地导游踢翻在地导致休克，招致舆论不满。</p>\n<p>@ccav77：@在西安: 13:30左右，美国“第一夫人”米歇尔一行来到临潼兵马俑参观，故此要清场。警察让照片中这个导游出去，导游说马上就走，因动作稍微慢了点，就被这个特警一脚踢翻在地导致休克。此事引起了周围游客不满…&#8230;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/03/BjfZ565CIAAZFxA.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-339762\" alt=\"BjfZ565CIAAZFxA\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/03/BjfZ565CIAAZFxA.jpg\" width=\"450\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/03/BjfZ565CIAAZFxA.jpg 320w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/03/BjfZ565CIAAZFxA-80x300.jpg 80w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/03/BjfZ565CIAAZFxA-273x1024.jpg 273w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18270,18269,10466,20534],"tags":[24888,9420,19988,24870,15845]}